{"tid":1441153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府係咪諗住用經濟差嚟瓦解民意","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T15:30:20.000Z","uid":146535,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5439da8350a61269a4a293b80cc5d0de44eb8875","tid":1441153,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"5/8 出嚟講野之後政府記者會做全面包圍<br />\n治安就話示威搞到社會混亂，再老屈示威者係極端暴力份子<br />\n呢個擺明係想勇武同和理非割蓆<br />\n出面淺黃同中立至淺藍<br />\n如果用經濟差，再痴埋5/8 罷工話堵路堵鐵<br />\n再出文宣同經濟差嘅數據痴埋<br />\n酒店業少左人又關我地事<br />\n亦係中國完全控制到<br />\n對外就話香港亂搞到少左人嚟講<br />\n雖然全部最後都可以歸因於香港旅遊業依賴左中國好耐<br />\n亦係佢地常用手段而且唔會陌生<br />\n但出面啲人睇到會點諗<br />\n佢地唔會知香港經濟下行係林鄭月娥上任之後已經發生嘅事<br />\n只知政府報導嘅「事實」就係示威加劇之後發生嘅事<br />\n連登以外嘅其他香港人又係忽然新聞迷被成功洗腦<br />\n<br />\n會唔會就係政府想要嘅佈局？？"},{"pid":"7732646870464c7a76c7fc0e90db1a316324adcd","tid":1441153,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"@2243 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=08b660b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCVXGRa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCVXGRa.png&h=471a367f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"},{"pid":"d01b3363d0f09347e2e63faa9d65c617e26f887d","tid":1441153,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZTeKhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZTeKhD.jpg&h=5a226166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pUtOKi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pUtOKi.png&h=81a60dbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/